      <div rend="slide">
        <head>Conclusions</head>
        <list>
          <item>even the simplest of approaches allows you to share your encoding, your
            analysis</item>
          <item>the more ambitious your markup, the more sophisticated the possibilities</item>
          <item>there is a common set of techniques and tools: you don't need to re-invent the
            wheel</item>
          <item>TEI XML empowers the data provider: you determine what can be done with your
            materials</item>

